{"id": 1775448189676, "text": "Yo, check it, let\u2019s take it back to the concrete, where the shadows weigh a ton and nobody\u2019s handin' out favors. Listen.\n\n---\n\nLook, I\u2019m fresh out the gutter, eyes bloodshot from the grind,\nTryna find a piece of mind in a city that\u2019s colorblind.\nThe feds tappin\u2019 the wires, the vultures circlin\u2019 the block,\nWhile I\u2019m just tryna make the world spin 'round the tick of my clock.\nMy sneakers worn out from chasin\u2019 ghosts in the rain,\nInjectin\u2019 rhythm in my veins just to numb out the fuckin' pain.\n\nThey say \"Sky\u2019s the limit,\" but the ceiling\u2019s made of lead,\nGot me lookin\u2019 over my shoulder, duckin\u2019 shots aimed at my head.\nThese fake-ass hustlers talkin' big like they own the throne,\nBut they wouldn't last a second when they\u2019re standin' all alone.\nI see the envy in their eyes, that green-eyed monster creepin',\nWaitin' for a man to trip while the rest of the world is sleepin'.\n\nMotherfuckers want the glory but they don't want the scars,\nWanna reach for the moon without lookin' through the bars.\nI\u2019m a product of the struggle, a diamond birthed in the dirt,\nBuilt a fortress out of heartache and a kingdom out of hurt.\nIt\u2019s a dog-eat-dog world, and I\u2019m the biggest hound in the pack,\nIf you\u2019re plannin' on crossin' me, better watch your fuckin' back.\n\nPour a little liquor for the homies lost to the street,\nAnother name on a t-shirt, another body in the heat.\nLife\u2019s a bitch, then you die, that\u2019s what the O.G.s used to say,\nSo I\u2019m-a live it to the fullest \u2018til they carry me away.\nI\u2019m talkin\u2019 real spit, no filter, just the weight of the soul,\nTryna stay golden in a world that\u2019s turnin' black as coal.\n\nSo keep your \"he-said, she-said,\" keep your weak-ass lies,\nI can see the truth burnin\u2019 deep behind your disguise. \nI\u2019m a king without a crown, a soldier without a war, \nJust a man against the world, wonderin' what I\u2019m livin' for.\nBut as long as I\u2019m breathin\u2019, as long as my heart beats true,\nI\u2019m-a keep kickin' this realness\u2014fuck what you\u2019re tryna do.\n\nWord is bond. I\u2019m out.", "voice": "am_adam", "duration": 107.904, "filename": "audio_1775448189676.wav", "word_timings": [{"word": "Yo,", "start": 0.0, "end": 0.3}, {"word": "check", "start": 0.3, "end": 0.59}, {"word": "it,", "start": 0.59, "end": 0.89}, {"word": "let\u2019s", "start": 0.89, "end": 1.19}, {"word": "take", "start": 1.19, "end": 1.48}, {"word": "it", "start": 1.48, "end": 1.78}, {"word": "back", "start": 1.78, "end": 2.08}, {"word": "to", "start": 2.08, "end": 2.37}, {"word": "the", "start": 2.37, "end": 2.67}, {"word": "concrete,", "start": 2.67, "end": 2.96}, {"word": "where", "start": 2.96, "end": 3.26}, {"word": "the", "start": 3.26, "end": 3.56}, {"word": "shadows", "start": 3.56, "end": 3.85}, {"word": "weigh", "start": 3.85, "end": 4.15}, {"word": "a", "start": 4.15, "end": 4.45}, {"word": "ton", "start": 4.45, "end": 4.74}, {"word": "and", "start": 4.74, "end": 5.04}, {"word": "nobody\u2019s", "start": 5.04, "end": 5.34}, {"word": "handin'", "start": 5.34, "end": 5.63}, {"word": "out", "start": 5.63, "end": 5.93}, {"word": "favors.", "start": 5.93, "end": 6.23}, {"word": "Listen.", "start": 6.23, "end": 6.52}, {"word": "---", "start": 6.52, "end": 6.82}, {"word": "Look,", "start": 6.82, "end": 7.11}, {"word": "I\u2019m", "start": 7.11, "end": 7.41}, {"word": "fresh", "start": 7.41, "end": 7.71}, {"word": "out", "start": 7.71, "end": 8.0}, {"word": "the", "start": 8.0, "end": 8.3}, {"word": "gutter,", "start": 8.3, "end": 8.6}, {"word": "eyes", "start": 8.6, "end": 8.89}, {"word": "bloodshot", "start": 8.89, "end": 9.19}, {"word": "from", "start": 9.19, "end": 9.49}, {"word": "the", "start": 9.49, "end": 9.78}, {"word": "grind,", "start": 9.78, "end": 10.08}, {"word": "Tryna", "start": 10.08, "end": 10.38}, {"word": "find", "start": 10.38, "